name: Gslabs
body:
### Open APIs are a Code Pirate's Playground

Get Satisfaction's open API means there are endless possibilities for what can be built to make your community even more awesome. On this site, you'll find examples that have been hacked by others. Add them to your community to extend native functionality and admin tools, or use them as a jumping off point to inspire your own inner code pirate.

### The API is your oyster - go nuts!
